-- Novorossiysk Shares Rally as Port Reopens After Flooding
-- B y   J a c k   J o r d a n
-- 2012-07-09T06:43:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-09/novorossiysk-shares-rally-as-port-reopens-after-flooding.html
OAO Novorossiysk Commercial Sea Port
headed for the biggest daily gain in a week as operations
resumed after flooding.  The  shares  jumped 1 percent to 2.84 rubles as of 10:28 a.m.
in Moscow, poised for the sharpest advance since July 2.
Operations at the Black Sea port were halted for about four
hours on July 7, the company said in e-mailed statements the
same day.  To contact the reporter on this story:
